videos.description: With under five seconds to play and down by 2 points, Stetson's Divine Myles drives to the rim but is rejected by Zach Johnson for the win and a ticket to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Florida Gulf Coast wins on late block, punches ticket to the Dance

videos.description: Zach Johnson talks about his huge block that secured the win over Stetson and punched Florida Gulf Coast's ticket to the NCAA Tournament.
videos.headline: Zach Johnson a one-man wrecking crew for FGCU
